Uses of Package
com.min.utilities.convert

  • Classes in com.min.utilities.convert used by com.min.utilities.convert 
    Class Description
    AbstractConverter
    An abstract class representing a general converter contains the common data and methods which are going to be inherited and implemented by concrete child classes The concrete class includes but not limited to Length Unit Converter, Temperature Unit Converter, Weight Unit Converter.
    FactoryConverter
    This class build a converter factory in compliance with "Factory Design Pattern" All converters will be instantiated by the worker method createConverter() worker method in it.
    LengthConverter
    Build a concrete Length Converter class It inherits the abstract converter class It has its own fields LENGTH_UNIT_LIST, CONVERSION_RATE_IN_ORDER.
    TemperatureConverter
    Build a concrete Temperature Converter class It inherits the abstract converter class It has its own fields TEMPERATURE_UNIT_LIST It implements the logics of the abstract method convertUnits() inherited from the super class
    WeightConverter
    Build a concrete Weight Converter class It inherits the abstract converter class It has its own fields WEIGHT_UNIT_LIST, CONVERSION_RATE_IN_ORDER.
